steps.instruction:
Take US T-Mobile in home, and roam to Chunghwa telecom in foreign as example
the content in eu-roaming.json should be like below

{
  "home": {
    "310": {
      "260": true
    }
  },
  "foreign": {
    "466": {
      "92": true
    }
  },
  "defaultApns": [{
    "apn": "eu.apn",
    "types": ["default"]
  ]}
}

